query_result.query:
SELECT less_100::float /total AS less_100_ratio,
       trade_date
FROM
  (SELECT trade_date,
          count(CASE
                    WHEN CLOSE <= 100 THEN 1
                END) AS less_100,
          count(1) AS total
   FROM cb_daily
   GROUP BY trade_date) AS cb_less_100
ORDER BY trade_date DESC
LIMIT 1000
